                    The Sixth ACM SIGPLAN Workshop
           Programming Languages meets Program Verification
                     --- 2nd call for papers ---

!!! Note: Submission deadline updated to October 14, 2011 !!!

24th January, 2012
Philadelphia, USA
(Affiliated with POPL 2012)
